# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo AND in the working tree, on every
# platform. Without eol=lf, a Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) materializes
# CRLF working copies, which Biome (LF-only) then flags as format errors — while
# CI on Linux sees LF and passes. Pinning eol=lf keeps both consistent.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files git already auto-detects; make it explicit so they're never touched.
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.ico binary
